## Privacy & Security

### Is my data private?

Yes. All data is stored locally on your device and in your personal iCloud account. We do not operate servers, collect analytics, or share data with third parties. See our Privacy Policy for full details.

### Can I lock the app?

Yes. Enable App Lock in Settings > Security to require Face ID or Touch ID to open 2Lines.

### How do I delete my data?

Go to Settings > Delete All Data. This permanently removes all journey data, photos, recordings, and milestones from your device. This action cannot be undone.

## Troubleshooting

### My notifications aren't working

1. Check that notifications are enabled in your device Settings > 2Lines > Notifications
2. Ensure you've configured notification preferences in 2Lines Settings > Notification Preferences
3. Make sure the toggles for the alert types you want are enabled

### My Apple Health data isn't syncing

1. Verify Apple Health integration is enabled in 2Lines Settings > Apple Health
2. Check that 2Lines has read permission in the Health app > Sharing > Apps > 2Lines
3. Tap "Sync Now" in Settings to force a refresh

### My photos or recordings aren't appearing

Ensure 2Lines has camera and microphone permissions. Go to your device Settings > 2Lines and verify Camera and Microphone access are enabled.

